# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [1.0.0] - 2026-03-05

### Added
- Initial release of OpenCloud add-on for Home Assistant
- Support for amd64 and arm64 architectures
- Persistent storage for OpenCloud data
- Configurable admin password and domain
- Logging level configuration
- External proxy support
- S6-overlay process supervision

### Notes
- Uses OpenCloud rolling release (latest stable version)
- Configured with external proxy (no built-in Collabora, Calendar, or Contacts)
- Decomposed storage driver for file management
